definitions.definition: The capital city of Kansas , United States and the county seat of Shawnee County .
A village in Quiver Township, Mason County , Illinois .
A town in Clearspring Township and Eden Township, LaGrange County , Indiana .
An unincorporated community in Lawrence County , Mississippi , named after Topeka, Kansas.
